<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Magnanimous" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Magnanimous,</orth> dauntless, heroic: <cit><quote>be m. in the enterprise,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 3.6.70" default="NO" valid="yes">All's III, 6, 70</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>most m. mouse,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.2.171" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B III, 2, 171</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>as m. as Agamemnon,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.6" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 6, 6</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.18" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 7, 18</bibl>. <cit><quote>valiant and m. deeds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 2.2.200" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 2, 200</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.3.277" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 277</bibl>. cf. Armado's letter in <bibl n="shak. lll 4.1.65" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 1, 65</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>